    "body": "If it is goerli.cfg then the best chance to limit this further would be by changing\r\n      \"BlockInfosDbCacheIndexAndFilterBlocks\": false\r\nto\r\n      \"BlockInfosDbCacheIndexAndFilterBlocks\": true\r\n\r\nanother (more drastic change) would be:\r\n\r\nBlockCacheSize\": 128000000:\r\nto\r\nBlockCacheSize\": 16000000:\r\n\r\n  {\r\n    \"ConfigModule\": \"DbConfig\",\r\n    \"ConfigItems\": {\r\n      \"WriteBufferSize\": 16000000,\r\n      \"WriteBufferNumber\": 4,\r\n      \"BlockCacheSize\": 128000000,\r\n      \"CacheIndexAndFilterBlocks\": true,\r\n      \"BlockInfosDbCacheIndexAndFilterBlocks\": false\r\n    }\r\n  },",
